    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a fair-condition car, and buyers should have realistic expectations going in. The exterior shows visible wear including several scratches and minor dents that are noticeable upon close inspection, and the paint has faded in certain areas. The interior is functional but shows clear signs of use \u2014 expect worn upholstery, some scuffs on trim pieces, and general cabin fatigue consistent with a well-used vehicle. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some attention in the near term; we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting. This is a practical, honest buy for someone who needs reliable transportation and isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection.",
      "price": 16500.0,
