    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that gets the job done without the premium price tag? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives reliably, making it a great pick for practical, budget-savvy buyers! You'll find some signs of everyday wear, as you'd expect from a well-used car, but nothing that takes away from its core functionality. If you're after solid transportation with room in your budget for any personal touches, this could be the one! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself. \ud83d\ude97",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we're committed to giving you a complete and honest picture. The exterior presents well \u2014 the paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with regular use. There are no significant dents or rust concerns, though a close inspection will reveal the small blemishes you'd expect on a well-used car. The interior is clean and functional, with upholstery showing moderate wear on the seats and some light scuffing on interior trim pieces \u2014 nothing that detracts from daily comfort. Mechanically, the car runs reliably; the engine starts smoothly, all major systems are in working order, and it drives without notable issues. We recommend a pre-purchase inspection, as we always do, but we're confident you'll find this vehicle to be exactly as described \u2014 a solid, dependable car that's been used and cared for.",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Exceptional Mint-Condition Beauty \u2013 Like Driving It Off the Lot! \ud83d\ude97\n\nThis is the real deal, folks \u2014 a used car that genuinely looks and feels brand new! Every inch of this vehicle has been meticulously maintained, from the spotless interior to the gleaming exterior with no visible wear, scratches, or blemishes. Under the hood, it runs with the kind of smooth, responsive power you'd expect from a vehicle that's been treated with the utmost care. The cabin is fresh, clean, and fully functional \u2014 everything works exactly as it should. If you've been searching for a used car that skips the usual compromises, your search ends here. Don't miss your chance to own something truly special! \ud83c\udf1f",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, making it a reliable and practical choice for buyers who want quality without paying mint-condition prices. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a decent shine with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use. There are no major dents or structural concerns, though a close inspection will reveal the small blemishes you'd expect from a regularly driven car. The interior is clean and functional, with upholstery showing modest wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and door panels, but nothing that detracts from everyday comfort. Mechanically, the vehicle runs well \u2014 the engine starts reliably, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems are in good working order. Some routine maintenance items may be due or recently completed, and we recommend a pre-purchase inspection if you'd like full peace of mind. Overall, this is a solid, dependable vehicle that offers genuine value for the price.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
